items.name: sqlfang
items.description: 🚀 SQLFang 是一款用 Erlang 实现的轻量级 SQL 注入检测工具，专注于快速扫描网页参数，探测潜在的注入风险和数据库类型。适合想用 Erlang 玩安全检测的你，稳、准、狠。

items.name: Estudos-em-Python-
items.description: Este será meu repositório para acompanhar meus estudos em Python. Estou começando na programação e acredito que, ao criar o hábito de subir tudo o que aprendo, poderei ver com mais clareza minha evolução e progresso ao longo do tempo. Cada pequeno passo importa na jornada de aprendizado!

items.name: Riyadh-Metro-Dashboard-Power-BI
items.description: This project showcases an interactive Power BI dashboard built to visualize key metrics for the Riyadh Metro system in Saudi Arabia. It includes insights on ridership trends, on-time performance, and operational KPIs to support decision-making and performance monitoring for urban transit systems.

items.name: pyspark-stock-forecasting
items.description: This project performs stock price forecasting using PySpark and Facebook Prophet, leveraging 5+ years of historical data. It covers data collection, moving average analysis, trend visualization, and time-series forecasting, followed by model evaluation using MAE and RMSE.
